<p>Use our content guide to create inclusive content about:</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://service-manual.nhs.uk/content/inclusive-content/age">age</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://service-manual.nhs.uk/content/inclusive-content/disabilities-and-conditions">disabilities and conditions</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://service-manual.nhs.uk/content/inclusive-content/ethnicity-religion-and-nationality">ethnicity, religion and nationality</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://service-manual.nhs.uk/content/inclusive-content/sex-gender-and-sexuality">sex, gender and sexuality</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://service-manual.nhs.uk/content/inclusive-content/skin-symptoms">skin symptoms</a></li>
</ul>
